creator: RayLab
descriptionHtml:
This is the NextGeneration of Wallpapers for Otakus around the world. We bring you with all that an otaku can ask for: live, 4k and many more formats of wallpapers.


Everything is fully optimized for the best user experience. All of the images displayed in our app are user generated and collected from open-source servers.


Some of our app features:
> Automatic Changer
> Submit requests for new features
> & much more!


Please leave a review and don't hesitate to contact us if you have any questions on:
wallpapers.ra@yahoo.com


PLEASE NOTE:

This is an unofficial application.No infringement of original brands is intended. All of the wallpapers/images displayed belong to their respectful owners. This app only displays them from public, open-source servers were the creators have actually uploaded the wallpapers themselves for the public.
